data.description: Welcome home to this entertainer's dream! This stunning two-story all-brick home is located on the community pond/lake and checks all the boxes - open concept, granite countertops, hardwood flooring in the main living areas, guest suite, office/flex space, formal dining, and sun room separated with glass sliding barn doors on the main level. Follow the hardwood flooring upstairs to a spacious bonus room. You will also find the Owner's Suite upstairs featuring a tray ceiling and hardwood flooring and a sliding glass barn door that leads to a dreamy en suite bathroom and walk-in closet along with three additional secondary bedrooms - two of which have walk-in closets. Upstairs laundry for convenient living. The star of the show: the backyard. You will love waking up to breath taking sunrises over the pond, swimming in the heated pool, relaxing in the jacuzzi, entertaining on the extended patio, & watching movies on the projector screen.
